blog.title: “I’m sorry, Hermann. They’re in my head.”
blog.description:
{icon made by(I need to find the person who made it-)}

Alright, I think it’s time I finally edit this XD Hi! I’m Rae! But you can call me Sunny if you’d like, it doesn’t really matter XD I go by Rae online since I don’t like saying my name online to avoid creeps that could very well be on this right. I go by she/her pronouns, and I draw stuff! I don’t post art as often as I’d like to but I’ll try to post more if I can XD the fandoms that I’m in are wreck it Ralph, gorillaz, mystery skulls, fnaf, studio killers, Khonjin house, supermental, Dhmis, the furry fandom, mlp, Pokémon, 12 oz. mouse, undertale, athf, superjail, and a few more that I won’t list here to avoid making this too jumbled XD some of the ships I have are smack x pent(shelby), spagjin, erisol, lewthur, joecop(golden joe x peanut cop), Fitz x Rhoda, rectangular businessman x shark, undyne and alphys, 2russ, ignignokt x err, Oglethorpe x emory, master shake x ignignokt, and a few more that I’ll list in a text post XD don’t interact with me if you’re a homophobe, biphobe, transphobe, panphobe, or if you hate or have a phobia of anyone from the lgbt community. Also don’t interact or follow me if you’re a MAP, a TERF, or have anything to do with cringe culture. If you do have something to do with any of the stuff I just listed I will not hesitate to block you, and if you’re a terf or map I will not hesitate to not only block you but report you as well. And ESPECIALLY don’t follow me if your a porn bot!!!

Anyways, I hope you guys enjoy this blog! See you soon! 💛
